We are Bluetree Fruits Limited, a fruit and fruit‑related products supplier based in Hong Kong. We are now inviting quotations for a website revamp and related digital services.
Our existing website is hosted on our current platform in wix. We would like to:
Redesign and optimise information architecture and UX (categories, use‑case navigation, FAQ, etc.) to shorten the time users spend finding products and contact options, and improve conversion rates;
Redesign visuals and layout so the site clearly presents our corporate fruit hamper solutions, cold‑chain arrangements, client cases and brand story;
Add or refine bilingual (Chinese/English) content for corporate and individual clients in Hong Kong and overseas (especially Japan, Korea, Vietnam and other Asian markets);
Develop content marketing/storytelling pages, SEO and technical optimisation, e‑commerce features (cart, online quotation and payment), multi‑channel payment integration, B2B/export enquiry flows, logistics/fulfilment info pages, and Instagram–website integration with tracking.
Please kindly provide your rough quotation based on the above scope.
